== 出任劍橋大學校監 ==
2011年，盛博理獲劍橋大學校董會正式提名為[[劍橋大學校監|該校校監]]。<ref name="#2">{{cite web |url=http://www.admin.cam.ac.uk/news/dp/2011051901 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2013-02-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110626082048/http://www.admin.cam.ac.uk/news/dp/2011051901 |archivedate=2011-06-26 }}</ref>若在6月17日以前無人提出參選競逐，盛博理即可在7月1日赴任。<ref name="#2"/>但當地一間雜貨店店主抗議森寶利計劃進駐故憤而與5月29日提出參選。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.varsity.co.uk/news/3625 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2015-01-23 |archive-date=2019-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190612013039/https://www.varsity.co.uk/news/3625 |dead-url=no }}</ref>四日後，一群劍橋校友另擬出{{Tsl|en|Brian Blessed|布賴恩·布萊斯德}}為參選代表。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cambridge-news.co.uk/Home/Brian-is-blessed-with-50-backers-02062011.htm |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-06-10 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110610125725/http://www.cambridge-news.co.uk/Home/Brian-is-blessed-with-50-backers-02062011.htm |archivedate=2011-06-10 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-cambridgeshire-13640487 | work=BBC News | title=Brian Blessed bids to be Cambridge chancellor | date=3 June 2011 | accessdate=2015-01-23 | archive-date=2021-07-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210701193507/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-cambridgeshire-13640487 | dead-url=no }}</ref>6月20日，支持社會主義的[[大律師|大律師]]申請參選成為第三位反對盛博理的候選人。這次選舉是自1847年最後一次投票競選，劍橋136年以來首次需作選舉的遴選。最終盛博理在10月14-15日的選舉<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.admin.cam.ac.uk/chancellorship/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2015-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110924035330/http://www.admin.cam.ac.uk/chancellorship/ |archive-date=2011-09-24 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>中取得52%選票（2893/5558，± 2.5%）勝出，並於10月16日履新。<ref name="varsity.co.uk"/> 

